# Mark binary files explicitly so git status / diff don't try to text-
# compare them. The actual cure for concurrent-CI rebase conflicts on
# these files is the shared "worldscope-state" concurrency group across
# the workflows that mutate them — see the comment at the top of
# .github/workflows/daily-brief.yml.
*.sqlite                       -text -diff
*.png                          -text -diff
*.jpg                          -text -diff
*.pdf                          -text -diff
*.zip                          -text -diff
